doc.previous: In flight Wi Fi utilizing the T Mobile systems is available on the Boeing 777 300ER once the plane reaches cruising altitude Passengers can enjoy internet connection by paying through the system 41
doc.after: China Airlines publishes a total of 3 in flight magazines for its passengers DYNASTY Fantasy Sky and Sky Boutique  DYNASTY the China Airlines magazine has articles in English Chinese and Japanese The articles feature local and international events descriptive culture social introductions personal interviews in flight entertainment instructions and China Airlines news
